# sandbox Dockerfile + harness, copied from the pinned @soroush.tech/bench
# devDependency via `npm run vendor`) is committed: the Release workflow
# regenerates both and layers them onto the release tag's commit (see
# .github/workflows/release.yml), so main stays TypeScript-only.
